星级挑战 #2 – February 2019
  • 星级挑战 #2 was the first 星级挑战 to include 射击效果 among the standard prizes. It also featured the brand-new 激光炮遗产皮肤 at the final tier and was the only way to obtain it. This 星级挑战 lasted for exactly 1 month, beginning on February 1st, 2019, and ending on March 1st, 2019.
